    "title": "Career Opportunity Financial Analyst at Care Ratings Capital India",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Financial Analyst with drive and ambition, Care Ratings Capital India in Amritsar is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Care Ratings Capital India:\nCare Ratings Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Care Ratings Capital India!",
